**LIX readability score calculator:** https://www.ils.uio.no/hjelpemidler/lesbarhetsindekser/lixtest/

**Text analysis:**

* Number of words: 52
* Number of long words (more than 6 letters): 24
* Number of sentences: 6

**LIX score calculation:**

```
LIX = (Number of words / Number of sentences) + (Number of long words / Number of words) * 100
```

```
LIX = (52 / 6) + (24 / 52) * 100
```

```
LIX = 8.67 + 46.15
```

```
LIX = 54.82
```

**Result:**

LIX = 54.82